38int
39dwarf_get_globals(Dwarf_Debug dbg, Dwarf_Global **globals,
40 Dwarf_Signed *ret_count, Dwarf_Error *error)
41{
42 Dwarf_Section *ds;
43 int ret;
44
45 if (dbg == NULL || globals == NULL || ret_count == NULL) {
46 DWARF_SET_ERROR(dbg, error, DW_DLE_ARGUMENT);
47 return (DW_DLV_ERROR);
48 }
49
50 if (dbg->dbg_globals == NULL) {
51 if ((ds = _dwarf_find_section(dbg, ".debug_pubnames")) != NULL) {
52 ret = _dwarf_nametbl_init(dbg, &dbg->dbg_globals, ds,
53 error);
54 if (ret != DW_DLE_NONE)
55 return (DW_DLV_ERROR);
56 }
57 if (dbg->dbg_globals == NULL) {
58 DWARF_SET_ERROR(dbg, error, DW_DLE_NO_ENTRY);
59 return (DW_DLV_NO_ENTRY);
60 }
61 }
62
63 *globals = dbg->dbg_globals->ns_array;
64 *ret_count = dbg->dbg_globals->ns_len;
65
66 return (DW_DLV_OK);
67}
